1
00:00:10,350 --> 00:00:12,550
You saw Zhuoyi while following Ding Xi?

2
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:17,180
At first, I didn't want to believe it.

3
00:00:17,190 --> 00:00:18,990
But it really was him.

4
00:00:19,380 --> 00:00:20,190
And...

5
00:00:20,780 --> 00:00:22,040
they acted very close.

6
00:00:26,630 --> 00:00:29,220
If he came to Tang City to find Yin Lei,

7
00:00:30,110 --> 00:00:32,110
why didn't he inform us beforehand?

8
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:33,220
Could it be...

9
00:00:33,440 --> 00:00:34,990
he's like Zhang Chongzheng,

10
00:00:34,990 --> 00:00:36,850
also being targeted by One Heart?

11
00:00:39,190 --> 00:00:40,870
And Ding Xi is the honeytrap.

12
00:00:44,430 --> 00:00:45,710
Find out everything

13
00:00:45,730 --> 00:00:48,260
between Zhuoyi and Ding Xi,
past and present.

14
00:00:51,360 --> 00:00:55,280
[Your Sunshine]

15
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:57,200
[Episode 19: A monster]

16
00:00:58,220 --> 00:00:59,610
Here are the contract terms.

17
00:00:59,610 --> 00:01:01,340
Please have a look, Commander.

18
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:09,320
I heard

19
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:12,670
you've also been courting Zhang Chongzheng
from the Water Resources Bureau.

20
00:01:12,670 --> 00:01:13,930
You're a businessman.

21
00:01:14,030 --> 00:01:16,590
Preparing
for both water and rail transport—

22
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,600
that is understandable.

23
00:01:19,910 --> 00:01:21,180
You mean...

24
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,400
I

25
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:27,520
hate playing both sides most.

26
00:01:28,230 --> 00:01:29,470
If you want my railway,

27
00:01:29,470 --> 00:01:31,440
I must be your only choice.

28
00:01:33,789 --> 00:01:34,910
I believe in

29
00:01:35,060 --> 00:01:36,860
your sincerity, Commander Yin.

30
00:01:37,020 --> 00:01:40,350
But you're not satisfied
with our collaboration proposal.

31
00:01:40,430 --> 00:01:41,580
Ding Xi,

32
00:01:43,050 --> 00:01:44,479
you failed to deliver.

33
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:47,590
Yes.

34
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,570
I failed to convey

35
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:51,330
your intentions to him in time.

36
00:01:54,350 --> 00:01:55,210
Commander Yin,

37
00:01:55,259 --> 00:01:56,060
Prie...

38
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:05,940
I can help you transport the liquor here.

39
00:02:06,820 --> 00:02:09,280
And I can help you
infiltrate all of Hai City.

40
00:02:10,889 --> 00:02:12,890
I've got the distribution network.

41
00:02:15,210 --> 00:02:16,280
Looks like

42
00:02:17,990 --> 00:02:20,600
this contract
isn't getting signed after all.

43
00:02:24,270 --> 00:02:25,430
The contract is wet.

44
00:02:25,450 --> 00:02:26,910
We can draw up another one.

45
00:02:27,420 --> 00:02:28,770
I must be

46
00:02:29,490 --> 00:02:30,880
your only choice.

47
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:43,350
Commander Yin,
you truly have majestic demeanor.

48
00:02:47,570 --> 00:02:48,570
I'll consider

49
00:02:48,670 --> 00:02:49,870
your terms.

50
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,579
[Golden Pleasure]

51
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:18,150
Tomorrow is the day Zhang Chongzheng

52
00:03:18,150 --> 00:03:19,510
meets with Priest.

53
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,740
Take some men and station them
at the entrance of Golden Pleasure

54
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:23,070
and in the alley nearby.

55
00:03:23,170 --> 00:03:24,200
Stay on standby.

56
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:26,030
Brother Zhuofeng, don't worry.

57
00:03:26,030 --> 00:03:27,620
Half the coachmen and vendors
outside Golden Pleasure

58
00:03:27,620 --> 00:03:28,740
are our people.

59
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,000
Priest.

60
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:40,200
Let's get straight to the point.

61
00:03:44,340 --> 00:03:45,270
Director Zhang,

62
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,810
please take a look at the contract.

63
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:56,360
According to our discussions,

64
00:03:56,510 --> 00:03:59,240
I agreed to offer you
one year of waterway access.

65
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:01,560
Why does the contract now say five years?

66
00:04:02,230 --> 00:04:03,160
Director Zhang,

67
00:04:03,530 --> 00:04:05,180
one year is too short—

68
00:04:05,510 --> 00:04:06,970
gone in the blink of an eye.

69
00:04:07,570 --> 00:04:09,450
We'd like to work with you

70
00:04:09,530 --> 00:04:10,970
for a bit longer.

71
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,520
Using my authority

72
00:04:12,550 --> 00:04:14,340
to get your goods into Hai City

73
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:16,480
already carries significant risk.

74
00:04:16,670 --> 00:04:17,990
If we make it five years,

75
00:04:17,990 --> 00:04:18,920
that could very well

76
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,480
cost me my life.

77
00:04:21,209 --> 00:04:23,940
Do you have a better suggestion,
Director Zhang?

78
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:26,390
I'm not afraid of taking risks,

79
00:04:27,210 --> 00:04:28,700
but the profit split

80
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:30,290
needs to be renegotiated.

81
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:33,680
For every shipment
that goes through my waterway,

82
00:04:34,230 --> 00:04:35,580
at least this much.

83
00:04:36,230 --> 00:04:37,680
And the shipping schedule—

84
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,680
I'll decide that.

85
00:04:39,550 --> 00:04:40,550
Director Zhang,

86
00:04:41,110 --> 00:04:43,110
you're putting me in a tough spot.

87
00:04:43,310 --> 00:04:44,990
The choice is yours.

88
00:04:45,310 --> 00:04:46,600
If you're willing,

89
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,850
we can sign the contract right now.

90
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,920
I'm a businessman.

91
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:52,480
Business

92
00:04:52,870 --> 00:04:54,800
is about mutual benefits

93
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:56,280
and about

94
00:04:56,790 --> 00:04:58,030
give and take.

95
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:01,630
Director Zhang,
since you've laid your cards on the table,

96
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:02,630
I...

97
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:05,680
can't make a losing deal either.

98
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,990
In that case,

99
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,530
give it some more thought, Priest.

100
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,350
Goodbye.

101
00:05:31,550 --> 00:05:32,210
Daisy Wild,

102
00:05:32,230 --> 00:05:32,870
let's go.

103
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:51,870
Stop!

104
00:05:52,550 --> 00:05:53,880
Take care of her too.

105
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,030
Lu Ye!

106
00:06:59,810 --> 00:07:01,140
Young Master Zhuofeng,

107
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:03,500
so you had it all planned out long ago.

108
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,710
Don't let them escape!

109
00:08:55,190 --> 00:08:55,920
Let's go.

110
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:34,900
[Meiqi Grand Theater]

111
00:09:53,820 --> 00:09:54,670
Do you remember the first time

112
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:56,280
I forced you to kill someone?

113
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:59,360
You couldn't even hold the dagger steady.

114
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:01,280
Now your grip is firm,

115
00:10:05,540 --> 00:10:07,470
but your body is covered in wounds.

116
00:10:08,070 --> 00:10:09,670
And now you're trapped here,

117
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:12,040
about to die with me.

118
00:10:21,070 --> 00:10:22,870
You taught me how to hold a dagger

119
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:25,120
and how to take control of my own life.

120
00:10:26,470 --> 00:10:27,280
Master,

121
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,520
we won't be trapped.

122
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:32,220
Let's fight our way out together.

123
00:10:46,270 --> 00:10:47,750
I'm not your master.

124
00:10:49,340 --> 00:10:50,700
I even kind of hate

125
00:10:51,350 --> 00:10:53,750
that damned "Brother-in-law" you call me.

126
00:10:55,190 --> 00:10:57,190
What I didn't get to say last time is—

127
00:10:59,590 --> 00:11:00,670
I like you.

128
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:07,460
♪ How many people in this world
love across great divides ♪

129
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:11,580
♪ Like waiting for migratory birds that
never return, trapped in eternal winter ♪

130
00:11:11,580 --> 00:11:12,670
I like the way

131
00:11:13,830 --> 00:11:13,880
you conjure stars for me in the darkness.

132
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:20,470
♪ That sea guards the mountains,
burning with every wave ♪

133
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:24,150
♪ Only then may fate show mercy ♪

134
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:24,980
You...

135
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:33,060
♪ How strange,
meeting and parting, like accidents ♪

136
00:11:33,090 --> 00:11:39,260
♪ Like glimpsing light,
yet unable to hold it ♪

137
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:44,770
♪ Half my world is dust ♪

138
00:11:44,990 --> 00:11:53,350
♪ But I was lucky to have
seen the purest white in you ♪

139
00:11:53,780 --> 00:11:58,710
♪ Must we always have regret
to be complete? ♪

140
00:11:58,740 --> 00:12:01,890
♪ So mismatched we can't fit ♪

141
00:12:01,980 --> 00:12:05,100
♪ Yet we still met—how cruel ♪

142
00:12:05,130 --> 00:12:08,690
♪ I tried to understand and become ♪

143
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:12,190
♪ The rose they all praise ♪

144
00:12:12,210 --> 00:12:14,080
♪ But worldly tastes make people dull ♪

145
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:16,310
If we make it out of this alive,

146
00:12:16,970 --> 00:12:17,820
let's ride across the open plains,

147
00:12:17,820 --> 00:12:19,950
♪ And courage comes from ignorance ♪

148
00:12:19,950 --> 00:12:21,060
soar through the sea of clouds,

149
00:12:21,060 --> 00:12:22,120
♪ Even if the wind never stops ♪

150
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,980
and live a life of freedom and joy.

151
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:26,100
♪ I'll cross the boundary of pride ♪

152
00:12:26,100 --> 00:12:27,060
Okay?

153
00:12:27,540 --> 00:12:30,670
♪ Follow across barren coordinates ♪

154
00:12:30,670 --> 00:12:30,720
Whatever you say.

155
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:34,410
♪ You shone with brilliance in that instant ♪

156
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:40,930
♪ Made me drop my guard and cry ♪

157
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:33,970
Nobody move!

158
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,500
Brother Zhuofeng.

159
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:37,720
Take Lu Ye and leave first.

160
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,920
I'll handle the rest.

161
00:15:26,920 --> 00:15:27,800
It's over.

162
00:15:28,310 --> 00:15:29,370
Give me the dagger.

163
00:15:38,160 --> 00:15:38,920
Give it to me.

164
00:16:16,470 --> 00:16:18,430
Do those wounds on your body hurt?

165
00:16:23,740 --> 00:16:24,460
No.

166
00:16:25,190 --> 00:16:26,220
Not at all.

167
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,280
I've seen you conjure stars.

168
00:16:58,280 --> 00:17:00,520
I've seen you let off fireworks.

169
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:04,480
But in the end, I turned you,

170
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:06,130
who were pure and flawless,

171
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:09,869
into a monster that doesn't feel pain

172
00:17:11,390 --> 00:17:13,069
and doesn't even fear

173
00:17:14,119 --> 00:17:15,710
blood.

174
00:17:39,660 --> 00:17:40,530
Lu Ye.

175
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:42,200
Lu Ye,

176
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:43,520
it's alright now.

177
00:17:43,830 --> 00:17:45,490
It's alright. We're safe now.

178
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:49,240
Wake up.

179
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:50,830
♪ I covered myself
with the quilt tightly and huddled ♪

180
00:17:50,830 --> 00:17:52,000
We're okay now.

181
00:17:57,020 --> 00:18:03,250
♪ Waiting for your good night
seems to have become a habit ♪

182
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:09,250
♪ Don't care if the flowers on the window
are in full bloom or not ♪

183
00:18:09,860 --> 00:18:14,960
♪ All I care about is when the sun sets ♪

184
00:18:17,030 --> 00:18:22,800
♪ So I split a heart into two halves ♪

185
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:29,480
♪ I want to be seen through by you,
but I'm afraid you'll get sick of it ♪

186
00:18:30,320 --> 00:18:36,310
♪ We miss each other on this deep night ♪

187
00:18:36,870 --> 00:18:43,300
♪ Is it a kind of romance? ♪

188
00:18:45,630 --> 00:18:45,640
I'm sorry.

189
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:51,970
♪ I keep waiting till it's getting late ♪

190
00:18:52,360 --> 00:18:58,470
♪ I keep sighing till the moon
becomes full ♪

191
00:18:59,010 --> 00:19:05,140
♪ I'll count to three
and wait for your good night ♪

192
00:19:05,170 --> 00:19:11,450
♪ On this sleepless night,
my heart is broken again ♪

193
00:19:12,570 --> 00:19:19,430
♪ Why don't we count the sheep
and say 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 to the sky? ♪

194
00:19:20,300 --> 00:19:26,080
♪ Then let's evade the stars
and meet the moon secretly ♪

195
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:30,080
♪ In the hush of night,
let's hold each other tight ♪

196
00:19:30,100 --> 00:19:32,900
♪ Let's sneak away together ♪

197
00:19:33,970 --> 00:19:38,650
♪ The Milky Way needs our help ♪
